Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是来探病的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是不想待在办公室里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次见到红老师可别再晕倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别提这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次 看鸣人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她完全晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着浑身是伤的鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手婆婆 我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 和鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像脸色非常红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连赤丸也嫉妒的超追踪力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找梦幻的微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是纲手大人亲自审问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水木还是什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能够找到大蛇丸的线索已经完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果他也是大蛇丸的弃子之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不知道佐助的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和水木拼命战斗 结果却是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人无法接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说纲手婆婆 没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不行就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人现在也无法专心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人一直都缠着她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能批准他去找佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就偷偷溜出了办公室…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果中了埋伏 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说好几遍了 让我去找佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说好几遍了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要修炼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色仙人不在 修炼不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸也好 佐助也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有他们的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有消息的话 我会去打听的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个不明事理的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手婆婆也是个不明事理的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 不错 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要再往前半步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田既然来了 也该多看会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是看看 也是一种修炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开饭了 开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了两位的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天陪我来这里特训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一个小队的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队里的同伴有困难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当然会出手帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有一个同伴突然失踪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定非常痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说鸣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帮帮他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然想帮他做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人也对鸣人说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办法倒是有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被称为梦幻之虫的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说很早以前就已经绝种了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为怕他绝种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们油女一族也停止使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 应该还有少数存活在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人 那个微香虫是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次使用微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也距离上次大战很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微香虫是虫使所用虫的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从卵里出生的幼虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一会儿就成了蛹 然后化羽成虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让它们去辨认气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使很微弱也能找到这股味道的来源
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的嗅觉是忍犬的几千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着超强的寻人能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过微香虫好像几年才产一次卵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年正好是产卵之年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在正好也是孵化的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子里还有佐助留下的东西 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让微香虫闻这个气味的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能知道佐助的所在地了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够找到微香虫的概率是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说并不高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计有10%的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在村子正处于非常困难的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是下忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能随便地自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞翁失马焉知非福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为红进了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也基本没任务可执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如去赌一赌这10%的概率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油女志乃 犬冢牙 日向雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在命令你们去寻找微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次由志乃指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 那边的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不让你去也不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只有让你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这可是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果找不到微香虫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就对佐助的事死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 可别食言哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个得意忘形的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次马上就要过来修炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶点就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下要去执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别拖大家的后腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个大转身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么走这么慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以忍者的速度走到微香虫的栖息地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要两天左右的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要一开始就这么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在我们到之前卵就孵化了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微香虫的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雨后的第二天早晨才会孵化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时还不会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 可是 万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本队的队长是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务中请听队长的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难想象你至今是怎么和那个家伙相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会和鸣人成为好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人他们刚才出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找虫子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志乃最合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有拥有白眼的雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及嗅觉超群的牙和赤丸同行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没必要再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下我的任务就是尽快成为医疗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天快黑了 搭帐篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经搭帐篷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点儿都不累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往前走点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 本队的队长是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经睡觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数动植物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日落则眠 日出则醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要寻找虫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须亲身去体会它们的生活节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 太阳才刚落山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 本队的队长是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早怎么可能睡得着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽这么说 竟然这么快就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了这么久 还没睡够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上起来小便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到一件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田也感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么个不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀑布里有个非常漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人挥手的同时 水也舞动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上去打招呼时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是做梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田的脸非常红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会真感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个果实可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就吃它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也能节约我们的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种人型大的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了会狂泻不止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哪个傻瓜会吃那么大的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马…上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是第一次看到这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不像人能生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以对虫子们来说就是乐园了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个比中忍考试简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 太脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为队长我有一个警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不说我也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要警告你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务完成之后 一定要好好揍你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是微香虫之森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里的话 说明他们的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝不会把微香虫让给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微香虫是我们上水流一族的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个照片的虫子我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 没想到这就是微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上在厨房里偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是便用拖鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的只不过是普通的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:22:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里不对了 虫子怎么看都一样
